12.733205Z	   25 Query	SELECT e.first_name AS employee_first_name, e.last_name AS employee_last_name, m.first_name AS manager_first_name, m.last_name AS manager_last_name FROM employees e LEFT JOIN employees m ON e.manager_id = m.employee_id

12.764673Z	   25 Query	SELECT d.department_name, e.first_name, e.last_name, e.salary FROM employees e JOIN departments d ON e.department_id = d.department_id WHERE (e.department_id, e.salary) IN ( SELECT department_id, MAX(salary) FROM employees GROUP BY department_id )
12.786702Z	   25 Query	SELECT e.first_name, e.last_name, j.job_title, e.hire_date FROM employees e JOIN jobs j ON e.job_id = j.job_id WHERE e.hire_date > '1995-01-01' ORDER BY e.hire_date
12.801940Z	   25 Query	SELECT j.job_title, AVG(e.salary) AS average_salary FROM employees e JOIN jobs j ON e.job_id = j.job_id GROUP BY j.job_title

12.816842Z	   25 Query	SELECT e.employee_id, e.first_name, e.last_name, COUNT(d.dependent_id) AS num_dependents FROM employees e LEFT JOIN dependents d ON e.employee_id = d.employee_id GROUP BY e.employee_id
